    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>courgette</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato[es]</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
