    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the vegetables are softening, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 550ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[825ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.1L]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
