    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>haddock bites</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for a further 4-5 min or until the haddock is cooked through and the orzo is tender – this is your <strong>haddock & red pesto orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
